<br>
Toll roads are another annoyance.  In one respect I like (a lot, a VERY lot) having the people that USE a resource be the ones to pay for it much more than via allocated funding from a big pot controlled by unaccountable politicians.  On the other hand the money collected in Tolls is not used this way, it is used as a part general revenue funds, making American toll roads nothing but the INCONVENIENCE of toll roads without the benefits.<br>
<br>
